works.description: You might when you come to know that it comes signed by Pete Rose, one of the game’s greatest players, leading in career hits (4,256), at-bats (14,053) and outs (10,328). BiddingForGood has teamed up with renowned radio personality Don Imus for an online event that will benefit the Imus Ranch for Kids with Cancer, the Tomorrow’s Children Fund and the CJ Foundation for SIDS. The items on the block include a unique $100,000 baseball signed by Pete Rose and Paul Hornung, an Imus Ranch Gibson guitar signed by Imus and a Johnny Cash signed guitar.
